{
  "ComponentID": "ILI",
  "ComponentType": "Color TFT LCD Display Module with Resistive Touchscreen and Integrated Controller",
  "Description": "This is a 2.4-inch diagonal color TFT LCD module with an integrated controller, RAM buffer, and a 4-LED white backlight. It features a resistive touchscreen overlay and supports two primary interface modes: an 8-bit parallel interface for high-speed operation and a 4/5-wire SPI interface for reduced pin count. The breakout board includes level-shifting circuitry for 3-5V logic compatibility, an onboard 3.3V regulator, and connections for an optional microSD card. It is designed to offload graphics processing from the host microcontroller.",
